{
  "stem": "23498.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the Germans and the police always found them, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what else was there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father had a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What you-- you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For the wood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "To break the wood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "How do you-- An axe?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Axe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had an axe, and it was like he would be in a trance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was working on that axe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was sharpening it up all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were petrified, and we didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was so energetic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, you not only stay, you lie flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whoever will come will be killed no matter who-- German or police, Polish police or Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No one will come out alive from this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That what he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was the way we survive until that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As long as-- as long as the actions were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had to move again because they said-- ah, my father went out after that action, and he saw there are no people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the first-- the first or the second, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyway from the next building, the number 11, where the window was overlooking, someone yelled from the last floor, we've got a invalid here-- to the Germans in German because they were mostly-- there were a lot of Germans who were brought to the ghetto and they were so stupid.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were from second generations already--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, Hitler won't do anything to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We've got sons in the army, because it was to the-- you know, they-- they were second-generation Jews, and they believed so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So whatever the German said, they agreed to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one German Jew from the fifth floor was yelling, I've got a invalid here.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
